---
title: block_validation (EIP-7934)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init
    q_init --> q_receive : node receives block from network
    q_receive --> q_encode : encoded_size = len(rlp.encode(block))
    q_encode --> q_check : compare encoded_size to MAX_RLP_BLOCK_SIZE
    q_check --> q_accept : encoded_size <= MAX_RLP_BLOCK_SIZE
    q_check --> q_reject : encoded_size > MAX_RLP_BLOCK_SIZE
    q_accept --> q_continue : proceed with remaining validation
    q_continue --> q_final : block accepted
    q_reject --> q_final : block rejected as invalid
    q_final --> [*]

    note right of q_check
        INV-007: Size validation occurs before other validation steps
        INV-008: Rejected blocks are never propagated further
        INV-009: CL gossip protocol does not propagate blocks exceeding 10 MiB
    end note
